  "content": "\n<p><strong>My Peachy Picks on Etsy</strong></p>\n<p>I love mint greens and teals, corals and peach hues during the summertime. Since we’re getting closer and closer to the warmest season of the year, I scoured Etsy and put together a collection of my favorite peachy picks from fellow Etsy shops. Maybe you’ll see something you like! Check out all the shops below!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Ava boutiquee\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/188228444/peach-lace-chiffon-flower-headband-baby?ref=tre-2726178676-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ava Bowtique</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Cara Mia Vintage\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/176756769/adorable-rare-vintage-1970s-emmanuelle?ref=tre-2726178676-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cara Mia Vintage</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Flower Thyme\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/93237945/peaches-cream-paper-flowers-modern?ref=tre-2726178676-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Flower Thyme</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Katie Scarlett Co.\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/130687661/georgia-peach-burlap-pillow-free?ref=tre-2726178676-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Katie Scarlett Co.</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Studio1040\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/162220775/183-cts-oval-cushion-rose-peach?ref=tre-2726178676-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Studio1040</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"PuppyCat Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/166154104/paper-straws-25-peach-and-navy-coral-and?ref=tre-2726178676-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PuppyCat Crafts </a></li>\n<li><a title=\"EmilyJewelry4u\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/127767938/fashion-double-layer-teardrop?ref=tre-2726178676-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">EmilyJewelry4u</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Mailbox Happiness\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/158795947/peach-bakers-twine-peach-divine-twine?ref=tre-2726178676-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mailbox Happiness</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"The Magpies River\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/161167053/beautiful-lacy-peach-white-bra-burlesque?ref=tre-2726178676-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Magpies River</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Swirled Peas Designs\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/121035529/shower-curtain-in-peach-paradise-floral?ref=tre-2726178676-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Swirled Peas Designs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"There Once Was A Girl\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/129122412/peach-wedding-peach-hair-flower-peach?ref=tre-2726178676-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">There Once Was A Girl</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"MLE Jewelry\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/158636196/peach-earrings-coral-earrings-glass?ref=tre-2726178676-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MLE Jewelry</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Tabletop Made\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/86631562/youre-a-peach-letterpress-printed-card?ref=tre-2726178676-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tabletop Made</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"This Loves That\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/182371227/peach-gold-glitter-scallop-canvas-clutch?ref=tre-2726178676-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">This Loves That</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wild Rose Herbs\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/123556783/natural-lipstick-lip-tint-balm-peach?ref=tre-2726178676-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wild Rose Herbs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Pineapple Bay Studio\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/178861897/watercolor-fabric-cherry-blossoms-peach?ref=tre-2726178676-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pineapple Bay Studio</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Head on over the the <a title=\"Etsy Treasury\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNjE3ODY3Ng/millions-of-peaches\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>treasury on Etsy</strong></a> to comment and fave your favorite items! Let me know in the comments what you like the best!</p>\n",
